00:21:11.960 --> 00:21:15.320 align:middle line:84%
And this, for me, is one of
the most exciting-- thinking

00:21:15.320 --> 00:21:18.570 align:middle line:90%
of time as a program.

00:21:18.570 --> 00:21:22.100 align:middle line:84%
So I wanted to introduce
