00:21:25.040 --> 00:21:26.330 align:middle line:90%
in this series.

00:21:26.330 --> 00:21:28.700 align:middle line:84%
So interestingly,
the characteristics

00:21:28.700 --> 00:21:31.890 align:middle line:84%
of time and the way it flows,
they all support this idea.

00:21:31.890 --> 00:21:32.690 align:middle line:90%
Think about this.

00:21:32.690 --> 00:21:34.550 align:middle line:90%
Time has a beginning.

00:21:34.550 --> 00:21:36.290 align:middle line:90%
Time has an end.

00:21:36.290 --> 00:21:40.080 align:middle line:84%
Time unfolds as events that
follow repeating patterns.

00:21:40.080 --> 00:21:41.690 align:middle line:84%
These are all the
kinds of things

00:21:41.690 --> 00:21:44.150 align:middle line:84%
you would expect to see
happening in a program.

00:21:44.150 --> 00:21:46.820 align:middle line:84%
The patterns of time
repeat on different scales,

00:21:46.820 --> 00:21:48.380 align:middle line:90%
just as they would in a program.

00:21:48.380 --> 00:21:51.780 align:middle line:84%
They reoccur as cycles, just
as they would in a program.

00:21:51.780 --> 00:21:54.590 align:middle line:84%
We can move forward and we
can move backward in the time

00:21:54.590 --> 00:21:57.500 align:middle line:90%
program by shifting our focus.

00:21:57.500 --> 00:22:01.320 align:middle line:84%
Meditative techniques help
us to do precisely that.

00:22:01.320 --> 00:22:05.630 align:middle line:84%
So I'm going to share this new
model, a new way of thinking

00:22:05.630 --> 00:22:10.850 align:middle line:84%
about time, that may help to
give you a visual image of how

00:22:10.850 --> 00:22:13.280 align:middle line:84%
it's possible,
why it's possible,

00:22:13.280 --> 00:22:17.310 align:middle line:84%
for you to see the future
before it actually happens.

00:22:17.310 --> 00:22:19.880 align:middle line:84%
And I believe that will
illustrate this idea of time

00:22:19.880 --> 00:22:22.020 align:middle line:90%
as a program.

00:22:22.020 --> 00:22:23.810 align:middle line:84%
So a recent series
of experiments

00:22:23.810 --> 00:22:25.580 align:middle line:84%
from seven independent
laboratories

00:22:25.580 --> 00:22:28.820 align:middle line:84%
indicate that the
human body apparently

00:22:28.820 --> 00:22:33.020 align:middle line:84%
can detect time and
events that have happened

00:22:33.020 --> 00:22:36.830 align:middle line:84%
before they occur,
randomly delivered stimulus

00:22:36.830 --> 00:22:38.240 align:middle line:90%
from the future.

00:22:38.240 --> 00:22:41.240 align:middle line:84%
Now, the phenomenon, we
would call this prescient,

00:22:41.240 --> 00:22:43.280 align:middle line:90%
as in feeling in the future.

00:22:43.280 --> 00:22:45.050 align:middle line:10%
In the paper that
was released, they've

00:22:45.050 --> 00:22:46.580 align:middle line:10%
got a new term for this.

00:22:46.580 --> 00:22:48.710 align:middle line:90%
It is called PAA.

00:22:48.710 --> 00:22:54.210 align:middle line:84%
And PAA stands for Predictive
Anticipatory Activity.

00:22:54.210 --> 00:22:57.300 align:middle line:84%
So let me share with
you how it works.

00:22:57.300 --> 00:22:59.870 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to invite you to
visualize in your mind--

00:22:59.870 --> 00:23:02.330 align:middle line:84%
or maybe you can see
this on the screen--

00:23:02.330 --> 00:23:06.440 align:middle line:84%
if you can think
of time as a flow,

00:23:06.440 --> 00:23:08.410 align:middle line:90%
just like the flow of a river.

00:23:08.410 --> 00:23:11.180 align:middle line:84%
So think of time like
the flow of a river.

00:23:11.180 --> 00:23:13.222 align:middle line:84%
And the river is moving
in one direction.

00:23:13.222 --> 00:23:15.680 align:middle line:84%
So in this case, I'm going to
say it's moving from the left

00:23:15.680 --> 00:23:16.620 align:middle line:90%
to the right.

00:23:16.620 --> 00:23:17.420 align:middle line:90%
All right.

00:23:17.420 --> 00:23:19.250 align:middle line:84%
Because we know
that time follows

00:23:19.250 --> 00:23:21.570 align:middle line:90%
what we call the arrow of time.

00:23:21.570 --> 00:23:22.370 align:middle line:90%
All right.

00:23:22.370 --> 00:23:25.700 align:middle line:84%
As that river is
flowing, if we were

00:23:25.700 --> 00:23:29.990 align:middle line:84%
to put a post in the
center of the river,

00:23:29.990 --> 00:23:35.480 align:middle line:84%
that post would represent a
significant emotional event

00:23:35.480 --> 00:23:38.330 align:middle line:84%
that will happen in our
lives in the future.

00:23:38.330 --> 00:23:39.350 align:middle line:90%
It could be a marriage.

00:23:39.350 --> 00:23:40.280 align:middle line:90%
It could be a divorce.

00:23:40.280 --> 00:23:42.590 align:middle line:84%
It could be a loss
of a loved one.

00:23:42.590 --> 00:23:47.660 align:middle line:84%
It could be an ecstatic,
joyous experience.

00:23:47.660 --> 00:23:52.500 align:middle line:84%
The key here is that it is
emotionally significant for us.

00:23:52.500 --> 00:23:56.540 align:middle line:84%
So if you think of the post
in the river representing

00:23:56.540 --> 00:23:59.360 align:middle line:84%
an emotionally
significant experience.

00:23:59.360 --> 00:24:02.930 align:middle line:84%
Now, you know that if
the river is flowing,

00:24:02.930 --> 00:24:05.630 align:middle line:84%
and when the flow
hits that post,

00:24:05.630 --> 00:24:09.470 align:middle line:84%
it will create ripples
around the post.

00:24:09.470 --> 00:24:11.660 align:middle line:84%
And here's where this
gets really interesting.

00:24:11.660 --> 00:24:15.230 align:middle line:84%
Some of those
ripples actually will

00:24:15.230 --> 00:24:22.440 align:middle line:84%
occur upstream before the
post is reached by the water.

00:24:22.440 --> 00:24:23.240 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:24:23.240 --> 00:24:25.050 align:middle line:90%
So you have the post.

00:24:25.050 --> 00:24:26.906 align:middle line:10%
The water is flowing,
creating the ripples,

00:24:26.906 --> 00:24:28.530 align:middle line:10%
but the ripples don't
stop at the post.

00:24:28.530 --> 00:24:32.960 align:middle line:10%
Some of those ripples
actually precede the posts.

00:24:32.960 --> 00:24:36.830 align:middle line:10%
Scientists believe this is the
way the program of time works.

00:24:36.830 --> 00:24:40.040 align:middle line:84%
Emotionally significant
events in our lives

00:24:40.040 --> 00:24:41.900 align:middle line:84%
are like the posts
in that river.

00:24:41.900 --> 00:24:46.430 align:middle line:84%
They create ripples that
move backward in space-time

00:24:46.430 --> 00:24:49.010 align:middle line:84%
and precede the event before
it ever even happened,

00:24:49.010 --> 00:24:53.060 align:middle line:84%
sometimes by moments, sometimes
by days, sometimes by weeks.

00:24:53.060 --> 00:24:55.310 align:middle line:84%
Now, where this gets
especially interesting

00:24:55.310 --> 00:24:58.700 align:middle line:84%
is, as you've seen in
previous episodes in "Missing

00:24:58.700 --> 00:25:00.360 align:middle line:90%
Links," the human body.

00:25:00.360 --> 00:25:04.370 align:middle line:84%
In 1991, science discovered
40,000 specialized cells

00:25:04.370 --> 00:25:08.720 align:middle line:84%
in the human heart that are
called sensory neurites.

00:25:08.720 --> 00:25:09.849 align:middle line:90%
The term says it all.

00:25:09.849 --> 00:25:11.390 align:middle line:84%
They're essentially
brain-like cells,

00:25:11.390 --> 00:25:12.260 align:middle line:90%
but they're not in the brain.

00:25:12.260 --> 00:25:13.400 align:middle line:90%
They're in the heart.

00:25:13.400 --> 00:25:17.330 align:middle line:84%
These sensory neurites
have the sensitivity

00:25:17.330 --> 00:25:20.660 align:middle line:84%
to pick up information
from the field.

00:25:20.660 --> 00:25:23.300 align:middle line:84%
And it is now
believed that it is

00:25:23.300 --> 00:25:26.720 align:middle line:84%
in our heart, those sensory
neurites that are picking up

00:25:26.720 --> 00:25:28.490 align:middle line:90%
the ripples of the events--

00:25:28.490 --> 00:25:33.440 align:middle line:84%
significant events in your life
and my life globally, locally.

00:25:33.440 --> 00:25:38.945 align:middle line:84%
And if we have the
sensitivity to acknowledge

00:25:38.945 --> 00:25:40.910 align:middle line:84%
and the willingness
to acknowledge

00:25:40.910 --> 00:25:42.800 align:middle line:84%
what it is our heart
is saying to us,

00:25:42.800 --> 00:25:47.510 align:middle line:84%
it's not surprising that we
can often pick up these ripples

00:25:47.510 --> 00:25:49.070 align:middle line:84%
and have a feeling
about the events

00:25:49.070 --> 00:25:50.780 align:middle line:90%
before the events ever happened.

00:25:50.780 --> 00:25:54.710 align:middle line:84%
We saw this on a mass scale
for September 11, 2001.

00:25:54.710 --> 00:25:56.507 align:middle line:84%
There are countless
reports of people

00:25:56.507 --> 00:25:58.340 align:middle line:84%
that changed their
plans, didn't go to work,

00:25:58.340 --> 00:26:00.980 align:middle line:84%
changed airplane flights
just because they

00:26:00.980 --> 00:26:03.110 align:middle line:84%
had a feeling that it
wasn't the best thing to do.

00:26:03.110 --> 00:26:05.030 align:middle line:84%
They had a sense that
something was up,

00:26:05.030 --> 00:26:06.640 align:middle line:90%
something was going to happen.

00:26:06.640 --> 00:26:09.272 align:middle line:84%
And I'll talk about
this in a later episode.

